title: BRIEF-WSE Admits To Trade Shares Of OncoArendi Therapeutics
text:
April 13 (Reuters) - ONCOARENDI THERAPEUTICS SA ( IPO-ORT.WA )
* ON THURSDAY WARSAW STOCK EXCHANGE (WSE) ADMITTED THE COMPANYâ€™S SERIES A, B, C, D AND F SHARES TO TRADE AS OF APRIL 12
